            "heading": "Return & Exchange Policy",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_WdBxUC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At <strong>Zaal Mart</strong>, customer satisfaction is our priority. If you receive a defective, damaged, or incorrect item, we're here to help with a return or exchange.</p><h2>Eligibility for Returns & Exchanges</h2><p>To qualify for a return or exchange:</p><ul><li>Requests must be submitted within <strong>7 days</strong> of receiving your order.</li><li>The item must be <strong>unused</strong>, <strong>unworn</strong>, and returned in its <strong>original packaging</strong> with all tags and accessories (if applicable).</li><li>Returns and exchanges are only accepted for items that are <strong>defective</strong>, <strong>damaged during shipping</strong>, or <strong>incorrectly delivered</strong>.</li><li>We do not accept returns or exchanges due to a change of mind, incorrect size selection, personal preference, or dislike of the product's color or design.</li></ul><h2>How to Request a Return or Exchange</h2><ol><li>Contact our customer support team through our <strong>Contact Us</strong> page or via <strong>WhatsApp</strong>.</li><li>Provide your <strong>order number</strong>, clear photos of the item, and a brief description of the issue.</li><li>Our team will review your request and respond as soon as possible.</li><li>If your request is approved, we will provide instructions for returning the item and arrange an exchange or replacement, subject to product availability.</li></ol><h2>Exchange Process</h2><ul><li>Exchanges are subject to product availability.</li><li>If the requested replacement item is unavailable, we will offer an alternative product of equal value or provide store credit, where applicable.</li><li>Customers may be responsible for return shipping costs unless the item received was damaged, defective, or incorrect.</li></ul><h2>Important Note</h2><p><strong>Zaal Mart</strong> reserves the right to refuse any return or exchange request that does not meet the eligibility requirements outlined in this policy.</p>"
